00026 /// \ingroup (enums)
00027 /// \brief
00028 /// The FdoLongTransactionConflictResolution enumeration defines the list of
00029 /// available options for resolving conflict.
00030 enum FdoLongTransactionConflictResolution
00031 {
00032     /// Indicates that the conflict cannot be resolved.
00033     FdoLongTransactionConflictResolution_Unresolved,
00034 
00035     /// Keep the data as defined in the long transaction to be committed,
00036     /// overwriting the data in the long transaction's parent.
00037     FdoLongTransactionConflictResolution_Child,
00038 
00039     /// Keep the data as defined in the versions parent, discarding the data
00040     /// as defined in the long transaction to be committed.
00041     FdoLongTransactionConflictResolution_Parent
00042 };
